  <refsect1>
    <title>Description</title>
    <para>
    <command>FLUSH READONLY SLAVE</command> Manually refresh the information about the read-only slave node in the pgxc_node table of the coordinate node.
    </para>
  </refsect1>

  <refsect1>
  <title>Examples</title>
 <para>
 Manually refresh read-only slave node information:
<programlisting>
FLUSH READONLY SLAVE;
</programlisting>
</para>
